The paper deals with video object segmentation, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with merging and refining object proposals, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.RO (Robotics).
